        "cooked": "<p>Hi there. I was wondering if anyone has got a list of all the entries of anims.hqr<br>\nI remember starting doing that myself, but I stopped at entry 152 because animations were starting to get hard to figure out by swapping them with Twinsens ones.<br>\n(by the way, I found a few interesting unused animations such as Twinsen flying on a malfuncioning proto-pack and blowing on Gawleys horn)</p>",
