      {
        "id": 357363,
        "name": null,
        "username": "Lawrence",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png",
        "created_at": "2010-05-01T14:36:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Big whoops! I didnt mention that Im talking about LBA2 here. Stupid me. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><br>\nThis is why I was surprised of seeing Gawleys horn animation in there, and the protopack animation is not the one from falling off a cliff, Twinsen actually flies but in a wobbly manner, sometimes quickly spinning 360.<br>\nYou can check those out yourself if you want, the entries of anims.hqr are:<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#117</span> Gawleys horn<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#122</span> Protopack malfunction</p>\n<p>So the list is still uncomplete huh? Ah well. It seems nothing has changed since the last time I checked. I could post all the entries I found out if someone wants/needs them.</p>",
