        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png",
        "created_at": "2010-05-04T19:19:42.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>All right then, this is what Ive got so far. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p><span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#89</span> Twinsen punching again<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#90</span> Twinsen punching yet again<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#91</span> Twinsen slashing with sword (aggressive)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#92</span> Twinsen turning left (aggressive)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#93</span> Twinsen turning right (aggressive)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#94</span> Twinsen standing in discreet mode<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#95</span> Twinsen walking in discreet mode<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#96</span> Twinsen walking backwards in discreet mode<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#97</span> Twinsen turning left (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#98</span> Twinsen turning right (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#99</span> Twinsen crouching (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#100</span> Twinsen slashing sword (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#101</span> Twinsen jumping X+left<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#102</span> Twinsen jumping X+right<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#103</span> Twinsen turning left (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#104</span> Twinsen turning right (discreet)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#105</span> Twinsen standing with proto-pack<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#106</span> Twinsen flying forward (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#107</span> Twinsen walking backward (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#108</span> Twinsen turning left (proto-pack, walking)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#109</span> Twinsen turning right (proto-pack, walking)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#110</span> Twinsen turning left (proto-pack, flying)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#111</span> Twinsen turning right (proto-pack, flying)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#112</span> Twinsen getting hurt (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#113</span> Twinsen falling part 1 (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#114</span> Twinsen falling part 2 (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#115</span> Twinsen falling part 3 (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#116</span> Twinsen falling in water? (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#117</span> Twinsen blowing on Gawleys horn (!!!)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#118</span> Twinsen jumping forward (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#119</span> Twinsen jumping backward (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#120</span> Twinsen jumping left (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#121</span> Twinsen jumping right (proto-pack)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#122</span> Twinsen flying forward, wobbling and spinning (proto-pack malfunction?)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#123</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#124</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe and walking forward<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#125</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe and turning right<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#126</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe and turning left<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#127</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe and walking backward<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#128</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe looking around<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#129</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe falling<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#130</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe dying<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#131</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe rising after falling from a small height<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#132</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe rising after falling from a great height<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#133</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe pushing something?<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#134</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe drowning<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#135</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe jumping (to activate a platform)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#136</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe looking to their right<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#137</span> Twinsen holding umbrella + Zoe looking at each other<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#138</span> Twinsen walking forward (triton horn)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#139</span> Twinsen walking backward (triton horn)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#140</span> Twinsen using triton horn<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#141</span> Twinsen walking (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#142</span> Bob walking (I think)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#143</span> Twinsen turning right (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#144</span> Twinsen turning left (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#145</span> Twinsen walking backward (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#146</span> Twinsen in an odd pose (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#147</span> Twinsen getting hurt, spinning and collapsing (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#148</span> Twinsen standing (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#149</span> Twinsen getting hurt (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#150</span> Twinsen spinning backward (space suit)<br>\n<span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#151</span> Twinsen getting hurt and doing a backflip (space suit)</p>",
